# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# HRPulse — Environment Configuration
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Copy this file to .env and update the values
# cp .env.example .env

# ── Database ──────────────────────────────────
POSTGRES_USER=hrpulse
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=hrpulse_secret
POSTGRES_DB=hrpulse_db
POSTGRES_PORT=5432

# ── Redis ─────────────────────────────────────
REDIS_PORT=6379

# ── JWT Authentication ────────────────────────
JWT_SECRET_KEY=hrpulse-super-secret-key-change-in-production
JWT_ALGORITHM=HS256
JWT_ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRE_MINUTES=60

# ── Ollama (Local LLM) ───────────────────────
# When running inside Docker, use host.docker.internal
# When running natively, use localhost
OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://host.docker.internal:11434
OLLAMA_MODEL=llama3.1:8b

# ── Service Ports ─────────────────────────────
BACKEND_PORT=8000
FRONTEND_PORT=3000
MLFLOW_PORT=5001

# ── Frontend ──────────────────────────────────
VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8000

# ── CORS ──────────────────────────────────────
CORS_ORIGINS=http://localhost:3000,http://localhost:5173

# ── Environment ──────────────────────────────
ENVIRONMENT=development

# ── Azure (for cloud deployment — leave blank locally) ──
# AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY=
# AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT=
# AZURE_OPENAI_DEPLOYMENT=
# AZURE_STORAGE_CONNECTION_STRING=
